---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

import ContactCTA from '../components/ContactCTA.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Ramzi BENMANSOUR" description="About Ramzi BENMANSOUR Lorem Ipsum">
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="About"
				tagline="Thanks for stopping by. Read below to learn more about myself and my background."
			>
				<img
					width="500"
					height="600"
					src="/assets/at-work.jpg"
					alt="Ramzi BENMANSOUR at work with a colleague"
					  style="display: block; margin: 0 auto;"
				/>
			</Hero>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						Hello, I'm Ramzi Benmansour, and my journey into the world of software development has been a continuous quest for knowledge and growth. I have a passion for creating innovative solutions and learning new technologies. My experiences in both web and mobile development have equipped me with the skills to tackle complex challenges.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						In 2019-2020, I embarked on my academic journey in Computer Science at the University of Paul Sabatier. During this year, I gained foundational knowledge in algorithmics, Python, and JavaScript.
					</p>
					<p>
						In 2022, I completed the Apple Foundation Program, where I specialized in SwiftUI, UIKit, and networking for mobile app development.
						In the same year, I achieved a TOEIC certification with a score of 885 points (level B2), demonstrating my English proficiency.
					</p>
					<p>
						From 2022 to 2023, I underwent training in web and mobile development (RNCP 5 - BAC+2) at LDNR, where I worked on team projects using various programming languages and technologies, including but not limitted to: C, C++, Java, JEE , Angular and android.
					</p><p>
						Currently, I am pursuing advanced training in web development, focusing on Java, Spring, and Angular10 for an upcoming diploma as a Concepteur DÃ©veloppeur d'Application Java Fullstack at DIGINAMIC Montpellier, expected in 2023.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p> 
						My skills encompass Java, JavaScript, and Python, with a focus on Java for robust application development.
						I excel in Spring and Angular for creating interactive user interfaces.
						I'm adept at HTML5, CSS3, and Bootstrap for responsive web design.
						Git is my go-to for version control, and I efficiently manage databases with MySQL.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<ContactCTA />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	img {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>
